prompts.prompt: Create a counter component that has a button to increase and decrease a counter every time they are pressed. Style the component with Tailwind CSS, including hover effects. Add this component to the index page. Implement a backend API with separate endpoints for increasing and decreasing the counter. Each button click should call the corresponding API endpoint. Also, initialize the counter value with an API that returns the current value of the counter from the backend. The frontend should be in React and the backend in Express.js.
